      <title>如何给自己的博客添加一个追番列表</title>
      <link href="/2023/12/04/bangumis/"/>
      <url>/2023/12/04/bangumis/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="步骤一"><a href="#步骤一" class="headerlink" title="步骤一"></a>步骤一</h2><p>使用 <code>hexo n page bangumis</code></p><p>在 source 目录里创建了一个 bangumis 目录，此目录下生成了一个index.md 文件，这是追番列表页面。</p><p><img src="https://imgbed.questbolg.asia/img/image-20231204040439773.png" alt="image-20231204040439773"></p><h2 id="步骤二"><a href="#步骤二" class="headerlink" title="步骤二"></a>步骤二</h2><p>使用 <code>$ npm install hexo-bangumis --save</code>在博客根目录下安装插件。</p><h2 id="步骤三"><a href="#步骤三" class="headerlink" title="步骤三"></a>步骤三</h2><p>将下面的配置写入 <strong>站点</strong> 的配置文件 <code>_config.yml</code> 中:</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">bangumis:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>              <span class="comment"># 是否启用</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">bangumis/index.html</span> <span class="comment"># 生成追番页面的路径</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">show:</span> <span class="number">1</span>                   <span class="comment"># 想看，在看，看完</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;追番列表&#x27;</span>          <span class="comment"># 标题</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">quote:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;生命不息，追番不止&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># 格言</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">color_meta:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#555&quot;</span>        <span class="comment"># 追番项元数据的颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">color_summary:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#555&quot;</span>     <span class="comment"># 追番项简介的颜色</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">bgmtv_uid:</span> <span class="string">你的uid</span>        <span class="comment"># bgm.tv的uid</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">download_image:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>      <span class="comment"># 下载图片并使用本地图片，否则使用bgm.tv提供的网络图源</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">image_level:</span> <span class="string">c</span>            <span class="comment"># 图片高清等级 (l, c, m, s, g)</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">lazyload:</span> <span class="literal">true</span>            <span class="comment"># 是否开启懒加载</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">margin:</span> <span class="string">20px</span>              <span class="comment"># 封面图的偏移量微调</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进入<code>_config.butterfly.yml</code>主题配置文件</p><p>添加</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">追番:</span> <span class="string">/bangumis/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa-brands</span> <span class="string">fa-bilibili</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> <span class="string">Menu</span> <span class="string">目錄</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">主页:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-home</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">时间轴:</span> <span class="string">/archives/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-archive</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">分类:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-folder-open</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">标签:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-tags</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">友链:</span> <span class="string">/link/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-link</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">关于:</span> <span class="string">/about/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-heart</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">列表||fas</span> <span class="attr">fa-list:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">追番:</span> <span class="string">/bangumis/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa-brands</span> <span class="string">fa-bilibili</span> <span class="string">+</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>代码后的<code>+</code>意为添加项，不应该被复制</p></blockquote><h2 id="步骤四"><a href="#步骤四" class="headerlink" title="步骤四"></a>步骤四</h2><p>在 <a href="https://bangumi.tv/">Bangumi 番组计划</a>注册一个账号</p><blockquote><p><strong><em>请注意！番组计划只提供管理ACG收藏与收视进度，分享交流，不提供在线观看、下载资源！</em></strong></p></blockquote><p><img src="https://imgbed.questbolg.asia/img/image-20231204041315459.png" alt="image-20231204041315459"></p><h3 id="方法一"><a href="#方法一" class="headerlink" title="方法一"></a>方法一</h3><p>进入设置</p><p><img src="https://imgbed.questbolg.asia/img/image-20231204041629708.png" alt="image-20231204041629708"></p><p>找到用户名，设置一个用户名</p><p><img src="https://imgbed.questbolg.asia/img/image-20231204041708861.png" alt="image-20231204041708861"></p><p>填入<strong>站点</strong> 的配置文件 <code>_config.yml</code>（注意不是主题配置）</p><p>将你的用户名填入</p><p><code>bgmtv_uid: 你的uid        # bgm.tv的uid</code></p><h3 id="方法二"><a href="#方法二" class="headerlink" title="方法二"></a>方法二</h3><p>将鼠标指针停留在你的头像上，左下角会显示你的UID</p><p><img src="https://imgbed.questbolg.asia/img/image-20231204042345445.png" alt="image-20231204042345445"></p><p>或登录 <a href="https://bgm.tv/">bgm.tv</a> 后打开控制台（快捷键 <code>Ctrl</code> + <code>Shift</code> + <code>J</code>），输入 <code>CHOBITS_UID</code> 后按回车，得到的数字就是 <code>uid</code> </p><p>填入<strong>站点</strong> 的配置文件 <code>_config.yml</code>（注意不是主题配置）</p><p>将你的UID填入</p><p><code>bgmtv_uid: 你的uid        # bgm.tv的uid</code></p><h2 id="步骤五"><a href="#步骤五" class="headerlink" title="步骤五"></a>步骤五</h2><p>更新追番数据：</p><p>​    使用<code>$ hexo bangumis -u</code></p><p>删除追番数据：</p><p>​    使用<code>$ hexo bangumis -d</code></p><h2 id="步骤六"><a href="#步骤六" class="headerlink" title="步骤六"></a>步骤六</h2><p>生成页面</p><p><code>$ hexo cl &amp;&amp; hexo g</code></p><p>预览博客</p><p><code>$ hexo s</code></p>]]></content>
      
      
